metadata.name: NOS Alive 001
metadata.description:
NOS Alive is a festival in Portugal where I performed this year and where I told a story about how I've been feeling regarding the world in 2022. The visuals for this show are now available as NFTs with original music from myself and art by Miguel Mendes.

3D Artist: Miguel Mendes
Creative Director: Diogo Mendes
Music: HOLLY
